"""
Simple application providing:

 * Administration interface to clear entire cache and view memcached statistics
 * Celery tasks to clear the entire cache.

Installation
------------

 1. Add 'djangoplicity.cache' to INSTALLED_APPS so that the templates can be found.
 2. Edit the projects urls.py and add something similar to below *before* any admin sites::

    ( r'^/admin/cache/', include( 'djangoplicity.cache.urls', namespace="admincache_site", app_name="cache" ), { 'SSL': True } ),
"""
